{"tid":341816,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸小說討論","createTime":"2017-07-31T06:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T04:04:01.000Z","uid":67836,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cce90c62faeb0493619a491ca88a9fc04a33feff","tid":341816,"uid":67836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:10:31.000Z","msg":"想搵中長既搞笑修真小說 自己睇過:<br />\n1.妖神記:4分 出左600篇就唔出` 掛住搞動畫<br />\n<br />\n2:地球遊戲場:5分 最初個設定係唔錯 加上佢武器描述詳細<br />\n但到後邊已經無新意 會悶<br />\n<br />\n3.完美世界:8.5分 起初會唔知佢做乜鳩 但愈睇愈好睇 有感人 有熱血<br />\n搞笑位都做得唔錯 打斗都幾好睇 結局太急 但有首尾呼應 曾經既對手為左佢死<br />\n果到真係好正<br />\n<br />\n4.無限恐怖:9分 唔洗多講 好多人睇過 我自己覺得好正<br />\n<br />\n5.異常生物見聞錄:無評分 因為仲睇緊 算係休閒搞笑 廢柴主角類<br />\n<br />\n大家有咩好推介?"},{"pid":"577ebbfe7cb6ce4dc948d76c67731d32354875fb","tid":341816,"uid":67836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:14:18.000Z","msg":"推!!"},{"pid":"d7d0bcb50103643383f497fd95a55fececbbcdbe","tid":341816,"uid":5384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:22:37.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打推薦<br />\n我以前睇嘅小說全部都係同一條formula<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇到灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n你小心畀狗吠你係五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15907e311455a2537cf2384610f4af050034c24f","tid":341816,"uid":67836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:38:34.000Z","msg":"咁香港既小說好少好睇 加上唔係咁長"},{"pid":"cf9f8cbcae805e9e74e56e8acfaeb9d0d182c28a","tid":341816,"uid":111343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:18:55.000Z","msg":"我都有睇妖神記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家又動畫又mobile gamer咁 都唔知幾時先再更新"},{"pid":"0d06862a6942cfd0b848bb25427a2c8b16bfb31b","tid":341816,"uid":67836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim